{"tid":2035230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"527 不如來個黎明行動 唔洗十八區 4 5區都好好  盡自己能力","createTime":"2020-05-25T18:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:04:02.000Z","uid":134033,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d22cbd3f95eca48441a15a12ea98a8d1a72ca965","tid":2035230,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:28:04.000Z","msg":"相信去到5月27日 <br />\n<br />\n好難會定到共識 出定唔出 出去邊<br />\n<br />\n而且抗爭人數未回歸 長期作戰 急唔來<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未達到共識既情況下  人數不足不均<br />\n<br />\n嘗試去圍重狗佈防既政總立會 係非常危險<br />\n<br />\n少一個手足真係少好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然要打國際線 要重燃抗爭既自由之火<br />\n<br />\n正面對抗  整體而言  如果保到命 當然好<br />\n<br />\n但保唔到命  被捕被打 壞處更多 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人數未夠 動員不足情況下 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如嘗試下 各位手足係番自己區 熟悉之地<br />\n<br />\n來次黎明行動 不管成事與否 <br />\n<br />\n起碼都唔洗過份損兵折將  <br />\n<br />\n又起到撚狗作用   make到noise<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且 527只係打細boss 惡歌法<br />\n<br />\n後面仲有好多路要行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n527 出就一定要出  但要保命為先<br />\n<br />\n唔失去太多情況下 作最低限度抗爭"},{"pid":"115bb2a23a6c12487f0b905a436c82a4b906560f","tid":2035230,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:34:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0dcbf34fb589bbc4e825c81f4918b90346aecec","tid":2035230,"uid":134033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"推阿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e130bd1836cf24b9207a43960c529d5868313bb5","tid":2035230,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7f81aed719a8132268b8c42a100fe7cc19d851","tid":2035230,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:38:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b56b102ffcee0389f40f5dc4b33c347886aa768d","tid":2035230,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"